# NOTE: The runtime CSP for entrapass.aboutcloud.io is set by a Cloudflare
# Response Header Transform ("EntraPass: Security Headers"), not by this file.
# This file is kept in sync with the Transform so the policy is reviewable in
# git, but editing it does NOT change production.
#
# WARNING: frame-src is absent from the production Transform. This causes
# frame-src to fall back to default-src 'self', which blocks iframes from
# login.microsoftonline.com. MSAL's hidden-iframe silent token refresh path
# is silently broken. Tracked as v0.1.2 work (add frame-src to the Transform).
#
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), camera=(), microphone=(), payment=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://analytics.aboutcloud.io; connect-src 'self' https://login.microsoftonline.com https://graph.microsoft.com https://analytics.aboutcloud.io; img-src 'self' data:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; frame-ancestors 'none'
